snippet.title: Best VGM 449 - Dragon Quest IV - Castle
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3DFJ5MWd7E

See also:
Best VGM 361 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_H42_mzLMz0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Dragon Quest IV
Castle
